asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Kyle
description: Take a seat, grab a beer, let's grab some weapons, some knobs. Whatever, have some fun with them, start stabbing each other. It's a party and I'm gonna throw a party. I do think one of the most frustrating things is reading video comments from girls. "Kyle is cute!" "Oh my god I wanna marry Kyle!" But then at the same time knowing that for the past three years I've not been able to successfully be with a girl. You know that I hooked up with Christina the day after I had done Sarah? So what if I'm short, turns out girls actually like what I'm working with. "But why dude, let's go out tonight? I want to get laid man, let's see if they'll still go for this short guy who's so funny!" I want it as consistent as possible. I want it every time I'm on camera. I want people to say, "Whoa that was really good!" But I think it's such an insane request of a person to be funny all the time. I wake up every day, and I have moments in every single day of my life where I question myself. "Am I actually still funny?"

name: Rad Muthaflufa
description: That Rad is one bad mutha  Shut your mouth!  Hey, just talking about Rad!  And you had better believe that he is. A nighttripper if you will, much more accustomed to the shadowy spaces with lots of heavy deep subs and frequencies. Some say he has been behind the scenes at some of the greatest live events, some say he has been just a spectator. Some on the rarest of occasions some have even called him a star.  He has no time for that though, too much to see and do these days. Using brews made from such natural staples as mushrooms and Kush, he transports to his locations in a black smokey puff, leaving behind download codes for acts on various popular platforms in his wake for people to pick up. Unlike a leprechaun though, catching him would not make you rich, but the experience and good times you would get from hanging around him would be priceless. Highly loquacious, he almost becomes the host of any shindig with ease. Almost a guarantee of a good time in his presence.  One thing to remember because of his extra transient existence is not to get spooked or freak out if he starts babbling to more people than you may actually see around, that would just be Rad talking to parties in other dimensions simultaneously. Who knows, maybe you will be lucky enough to meet them too when the time is right. He is not a bad Muthaflufa for nothin!

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
